  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241760/extras/87aa466b65d9729881700182c4565af2.poster.avif?t=1772648569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241760/extras/87aa466b65d9729881700182c4565af2.webm?t=1772648569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241760/extras/87aa466b65d9729881700182c4565af2.mp4?t=1772648569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive Monument Valley in RC Cars with crash test teddy bears in 10 incredible offroad tracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the strengths of 4 unique vehicle classes: Compact, Sport, Mud Plugger and Titan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The bigger the vehicle, the better you'll be able to tackle the challenging levels filled with interactive rocks, foliage and flaming wreckage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241760/extras/1bc9bc370cf687af43c15b66b7d3d1aa.poster.avif?t=1772648569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241760/extras/1bc9bc370cf687af43c15b66b7d3d1aa.webm?t=1772648569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241760/extras/1bc9bc370cf687af43c15b66b7d3d1aa.mp4?t=1772648569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241760/extras/87aa466b65d9729881700182c4565af2.poster.avif?t=1772648569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241760/extras/87aa466b65d9729881700182c4565af2.webm?t=1772648569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241760/extras/87aa466b65d9729881700182c4565af2.mp4?t=1772648569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive Monument Valley in RC Cars with crash test teddy bears in 10 incredible offroad tracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the strengths of 4 unique vehicle classes: Compact, Sport, Mud Plugger and Titan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The bigger the vehicle, the better you'll be able to tackle the challenging levels filled with interactive rocks, foliage and flaming wreckage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241760/extras/1bc9bc370cf687af43c15b66b7d3d1aa.poster.avif?t=1772648569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241760/extras/1bc9bc370cf687af43c15b66b7d3d1aa.webm?t=1772648569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241760/extras/1bc9bc370cf687af43c15b66b7d3d1aa.mp4?t=1772648569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
